column5: Come Experience East Dallas. Awesome Duplex close to White Rock Lake, Dallas Arboretum with Thursday Tribute Bands, just a bicycle ride to White Rock Lake plus Casa Linda restaurants+, dining, grocery store. Professional Xeriscape yard with native plants, Privacy fencing in back. Full Size Washer and Dryer. 2 bicycles and 2 helmets for you to use while here. Close to Baylor Hospital @ White Rock Lake). Goldfish pond. Rent Kayaks at the Lake. Enjoy East Dallas living & Restaurants.
